_json.description: Enjoy a crispy indulgence with Anna's Ginger Thins Cookies. These thin, spiced cookies are based on Anna's secret family recipe. A traditional symbol of love and goodwill, Anna's Thins are also known as Swedish wish cookies. To make a wish, place a thin cookie carefully in the palm of your hand and tap it gently with your index finger.
